Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.54,0:00:52.37,Dragon Ball 2,,0,0,0,, {\i1}Soitsu mitsuke ni yuko ze BOY{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.54,0:00:52.37,Dragon Ball 3,,0,0,0,,{\i1}¡Vamos a salir a buscarlas, muchacho!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.21,0:00:56.31,Dragon Ball 2,,0,0,0,, {\i1}Yokai henge mo buttobashi{\i0}
